videos.description: Eric Musselman says the way Arkansas was able to close the first half and start the second on dominating runs secured the 79-67 victory over the Tigers.
videos.headline: Musselman says Hogs put together key runs vs. LSU

videos.description: Arkansas pulls away in the second half to soundly defeat LSU and claim a spot in the SEC Tournament semifinals opposite upstart Texas A&M.
videos.headline: 4-seed Arkansas handles 5-seed LSU to reach semis
